## Why This Is Asked

Tests knowledge of production-grade model serving, stateful components, and zero-downtime updates under streaming data.

## Key Concepts

- Embedding sharding and stateful serving
- Online updates without stale reads
- Atomic model version swaps and canary deployment
- Observability, SLAs, rollback strategies

## Code Example

```javascript
// Pseudo-code: versioned embedding cache lookup
const version = process.env.MODEL_VERSION || 'v1';
const embedCache = loadEmbeddingCache(version);

function predict(inputIds) {
  const emb = embedCache.lookup(inputIds);
  return model.apply(emb);
}
```

## Follow-up Questions

- How would you test zero-downtime swap guarantees?
- What race conditions could arise and how would you mitigate them?

